{"tid":121210,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"阿喱聲音小甜故《Hillywood阿Tim的情慾九歌》","createTime":"2017-02-15T05:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T01:22:24.000Z","uid":71810,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c94a23df5cd63564a13bc7c9dbe6570419924be","tid":121210,"uid":71810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"阿喱 聲音小甜故<br />\n《Hillywood阿Tim的情慾九歌》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MusicOneHK/videos/1352220778181713/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMusicOneHK%2Fvideos%2F1352220778181713%2F&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9d929759\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MusicOneHK/videos/1352220778181713/</a><br />\n<br />\n#NSFW<br />\n#N年冇錄過廣播劇<br />\n#曾經有一段最真摯既偷情<br />\n#唔好問我邊個係阿Tim<br />\n#自己去Hillywood搵佢啦<br />\n<br />\n冇咩事我都係出返去做半個股票佬，那邊的生活沒那麼非人，但我不得不承認創作的高潮是贏錢也贏不到的，金錢只是have sex，創作才是make love。<br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝 #WY #TM"},{"pid":"5c054ffa56c1495ec235c9e534db500a40dcce3a","tid":121210,"uid":6739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbe3405851062cc5d6dd96a49dd6e32087dc7ac","tid":121210,"uid":33427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"大野先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d399da73da677796f881b5c9366421789d689cde","tid":121210,"uid":7167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"終於可以聽返大野先生把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af42e1f5ab567db29f16fcdd77c76101ca88ced4","tid":121210,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:43:18.000Z","msg":"真係阿喱？！<br />\n當年好鍾意聽大野禪寺"},{"pid":"b6bb4cec11b1dbd281228d55289b0e12e5102054","tid":121210,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"連登是咪已經過左聽過阿喱個age group?<br />\n<br />\nbetween，啲歌幾正，個故事要經歷多啲先會會心微笑。"},{"pid":"a8da9b10ec3e7bcf3cbe8e5f29321ac98b35280c","tid":121210,"uid":71810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"故事就比較中佬啲，未去到老坑，但又唔再係𡃁仔，𡃁坑故事，同啲廣告公司年中做既飛機稿咁上下性質，自己J居多，但做吓又冇壞咁囉。<br />\n叫做幫兄弟個音樂平台做啲啲content，當然做既過程中自己都想留個念啦。"},{"pid":"96c351b2419dfa5b761ed3ba51c3c29b13e98979","tid":121210,"uid":78494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"好懷念當年聽你同Leo 既嘟嘟大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89f4c62b361759ab05b7df32fae98645fadadc2","tid":121210,"uid":71810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"地點Hillywood就係最近班藝文L朋友最鐘意去既點，每隔一段時間就有一個咁既落腳地，由尖沙咀亞士厘道的My Coffee，到柯士甸路Phonograph，旺角FullCup，宜家又到界限街Hillywood，身邊既藝文L朋友變變都開始變晒Uncle了。"},{"pid":"f5336e05bcd68a5535bb3f9872a7583469b4296e","tid":121210,"uid":71810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好懷念當年聽你同Leo 既嘟嘟大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你地成日都話懷念所以先整返個甜劇咋"},{"pid":"1ed1efb17556bdebfc83204fd5d6ce75080ecf45","tid":121210,"uid":78494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好懷念當年聽你同Leo 既嘟嘟大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你地成日都話懷念所以先整返個甜劇咋</blockquote><br />\n新手有十皮野想入市 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0966531a470070ce39c8fe1ff3121cd21ee6aafc","tid":121210,"uid":71810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好懷念當年聽你同Leo 既嘟嘟大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你地成日都話懷念所以先整返個甜劇咋</blockquote><br />\n新手有十皮野想入市 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享經驗，玩得好，唔係因為你勁，係因為你定！<br />\n首先我要問你想玩邊飯？衍生？正股？定殻股？<br />\n你係新手唔係全職，咁你一定係買股嚟坐，而唔係daytrade出出入入。<br />\n點先玩得定呢？<br />\n你有10皮，你就攞1皮至皮半試吓學習操作，亦都要記住，你既購買力就只係皮半，唔好玩超過，咁你就定，因為有咩事total lost你都唔入肉，咁你就會敢坐敢贏，如果你第一下就10皮ALL IN，唔駛兩星期你就返人震走。<br />\n<br />\n好股日日有，建議你去下載 炒家 app，關注 kent哥 或 肥柱哥 或 馬田 或 Ming Sir，睇吓佢地有咩推介，因為佢地日日望住個市，同埋推得嗰啲都適合中線玩吓既。 <br />\n<br />\n先用皮半（15%），有賺當然好，如果買中嗰隻唔升，就用15%錢學吓咩叫嚴守止蝕，千祈唔好因為手頭上仲有85%錢就學人係咁溝貨。<br />\n<br />\n仲之唔好ALL IN，淡定，先會有錢贏。"},{"pid":"2f51cef4e5dbabd593dc8d9e870cc3e6a08aa372","tid":121210,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好懷念當年聽你同Leo 既嘟嘟大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見你地成日都話懷念所以先整返個甜劇咋</blockquote><br />\n新手有十皮野想入市 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享經驗，玩得好，唔係因為你勁，係因為你定！<br />\n首先我要問你想玩邊飯？衍生？正股？定殻股？<br />\n你係新手唔係全職，咁你一定係買股嚟坐，而唔係daytrade出出入入。<br />\n點先玩得定呢？<br />\n你有10皮，你就攞1皮至皮半試吓學習操作，亦都要記住，你既購買力就只係皮半，唔好玩超過，咁你就定，因為有咩事total lost你都唔入肉，咁你就會敢坐敢贏，如果你第一下就10皮ALL IN，唔駛兩星期你就返人震走。<br />\n<br />\n好股日日有，建議你去下載 炒家 app，關注 kent哥 或 肥柱哥 或 馬田 或 Ming Sir，睇吓佢地有咩推介，因為佢地日日望住個市，同埋推得嗰啲都適合中線玩吓既。 <br />\n<br />\n先用皮半（15%），有賺當然好，如果買中嗰隻唔升，就用15%錢學吓咩叫嚴守止蝕，千祈唔好因為手頭上仲有85%錢就學人係咁溝貨。<br />\n<br />\n仲之唔好ALL IN，淡定，先會有錢贏。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽甜故學炒股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf874915e32826f2b9aaf486209e33d09b19188","tid":121210,"uid":7167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好懷念當年聽你同L